channel.title: I downloaded a client, but I got one error
channel.description:
I downloaded EyreScape OPEN client V3, and I had one error, I had the same with endar, I don't know if there from the same thing..Anyway, When I try to run it, it says..
"Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassFoundError: EGUI"
And yes, I have the latest version of Java. I did download the file store 32, whatever. =.= Also, don't tell me to turn The EGUI file into egui, it won't work. People have told me twice to compile...Wth, anyway, I did.
Thank You for reading/trying/ANSWERING, :D Crashing~
